00:11:45,359 --> 00:11:48,726
Excuse me, sir. You left these at your table.

130
00:11:48,796 --> 00:11:51,822
Thanks. Uh... Lincoln Street?

131
00:11:51,899 --> 00:11:54,026
Oh, yeah, just go straight out on Sixth Street.

132
00:11:54,101 --> 00:11:56,035
I'm gonna write this down.

