00:12:31,172 --> 00:12:34,164
[Thinking] Discount Inn.

137
00:12:34,242 --> 00:12:37,006
Natalie.

138
00:12:38,579 --> 00:12:41,776
My car.

139
00:12:41,849 --> 00:12:44,113
Teddy.

