226
00:21:12,893 --> 00:21:16,954
"See, you have this condition." [Laughs]

227
00:21:17,031 --> 00:21:20,990
Oh, are you still staying at the Discount Inn, room 304? You left it at my place.

228
00:21:26,573 --> 00:21:29,838
Yeah. [Chuckles]

229
00:21:29,910 --> 00:21:32,674
- They treating you okay? - I don't remember.

230
00:21:32,746 --> 00:21:37,581
[Laughs] You know what we have in common?

231
00:21:39,586 --> 00:21:43,386
We are both survivors.

232
00:21:43,457 --> 00:21:46,949
You take care, Leonard.

233
00:21:54,168 --> 00:21:58,195
