1001
01:25:51,946 --> 01:25:54,813
- No, thanks. - It's for a lot of money.

1002
01:25:54,882 --> 01:25:57,817
Come on. Proceeds are going to charity. Help me out.

1003
01:26:02,890 --> 01:26:04,915
