1210
01:45:23,583 --> 01:45:26,051
But it didn't stick.

1211
01:45:26,119 --> 01:45:28,349
Like nothing ever sticks. Like this won't stick.

1212
01:45:33,059 --> 01:45:36,927
I took that picture... just when you did it.

1213
01:45:39,666 --> 01:45:42,100
Look how happy you are.

1214
01:45:42,168 --> 01:45:44,693
